{"tid":637226,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張獻忠「屠蜀」殺10萬人　吃人肉","createTime":"2018-04-21T15:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T13:17:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"9e98df63cfb087e90cc5dd983800b39fd7c09435","tid":637226,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:03:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180421/20368468?_ga=2.194968045.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F20368468%3F_ga%3D2.194968045.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435&d=NCDN%2BRr8j1hfn9LkkYcFGJUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=02464577\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F20368468%3F_ga%3D2.194968045.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435&h=6a34e468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180421/20368468?_ga=2.194968045.1192471861.1524322713-581282530.1504247435</a><br />\n<br />\n張獻忠「屠蜀」殺10萬人　吃人肉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180421/large/a1003a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180421%2Flarge%2Fa1003a.gif&h=0aeb9e30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張獻忠像<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張獻忠與「闖王」李自成同為明末民變領袖，同樣都是殺人如麻，軍紀極差。張曾「屠蜀」殺十萬人，姦淫擄掠不在話下，他還熱愛強姦婦女後將之殺死食人肉。後來他兵敗在雙江河被伏擊，金銀財富盡跌江中，成為歷史有名的「江口沉銀」。<br />\n<br />\n張獻忠曾為捕快，但犯法判死，後來被特赦才倖免。他在1630年起義，轉戰各地，曾號稱「大西王」，在1644年攻陷四川後登基為「大順」，以成都為京。兩年後清朝攻打大順，張兵敗攜寶逃離成都，沿岷江南下，但在彭山雙江河遭伏擊，金銀珠寶亦隨船沉入江中，成為歷史上傳說的江口沉銀。<br />\n<br />\n張軍紀敗壞，殺人為樂，後世稱為「殺人魔王」，曾「屠蜀」十萬人，在四川留有「七殺碑」：「天生萬物以養人，人無一物以報天，殺殺殺殺殺殺殺」。史書指張的軍隊不帶糧食，部隊好吃人肉，張每攻陷一城，要求婦女上半身穿着艷裝，下半身赤裸，待張興起便隨時強姦。待他玩厭後，便將她們洗乾淨殺死，吃下她們的肉，令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鳳凰網  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n大盜掘寶　證江口沉銀傳說屬實<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n新疆派奶　印洗腦紅歌　被轟毒過毒奶<br />\n<br />\n大盜掘寶　證江口沉銀傳說屬實<br />\n<br />\n明代蜀藩王金寶首出土張獻忠寶藏值37億"},{"pid":"b0654ce42a9296720dee1c40bcda6a8d999c4624","tid":637226,"uid":24140,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:06:13.000Z","msg":"未來支那內陸地區會係 張獻忠 既天下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72594bad8314f15145ac7c7cc650f9ba9a8e1ba6","tid":637226,"uid":73627,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:08:38.000Z","msg":"莖牽gor<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c28ebcfbfbc0aea0b6b82def1a39bbd5b2dfdcb","tid":637226,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:10:24.000Z","msg":"對新彊派奶有興趣"},{"pid":"c3baf68a05c00b64facee88a07ba4dd4c88ff8d7","tid":637226,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:19:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0566b479d5f17fefbcd25cc7b174823104ce102","tid":637226,"uid":98163,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b0654ce42a9296720dee1c40bcda6a8d999c4624","tid":637226,"uid":24140,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:06:13.000Z","msg":"未來支那內陸地區會係 張獻忠 既天下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:20:39.000Z","msg":"總係覺得中國內陸比起哈薩克 吉爾吉斯 烏茲別克 仲要落後同封閉"},{"pid":"dbaa1bb94f9062ee1a42a3796ff31e06d5474b95","tid":637226,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:22:55.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a69f4f3fd35bdd3e12f3f770ef56b9d18952fd70","tid":637226,"uid":150400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:24:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c15bff95a690ead900403c6f845a63e1ca61800d","tid":637226,"uid":117837,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:27:41.000Z","msg":"張獻忠，字秉吾，